{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 46615904, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "CERV-2024-NRCP", "title": "Call for proposals to National Roma Contact Points  for Roma equality, inclusion and participation", "publicationDateLong": 1700524800000, "callIdentifier": "CERV-2024-NRCP", "callTitle": "Call for proposals to National Roma Contact Points for Roma equality, inclusion and participation", "callccm2Id": 46615930, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43251589, "abbreviation": "CERV", "description": "Citizens, Equality, Rights and Values Programme (CERV)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43422638, "abbreviation": "CERV.1.1", "description": "Equality and non-discrimination"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["Roma and  pro-Roma civil society organisations", "Roma youth", "Roma women", "EU Roma strategic framework 2020 \u2013 2030", "national Roma platforms", "non-discrimination", "EU Roma strategic framework on equality, inclusion, and participation", "national Roma strategic frameworks", "inclusion", "National Roma Contact Points", "Roma", "active engagement of Roma", "EURSF", "CERV-2024-NRCP", "equality"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "CERV-LS CERV Lump Sum Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43249821, "abbreviation": "CERV-AG-LS", "description": "CERV Lump Sum Grant"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "19 December 2023", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["10 April 2024"]}], "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Feb 27, 2024 5:24:57 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Feb 27, 2024 5:24:57 PM", "content": "<p>&nbsp;The deadline for submission of proposals to the CERV-2024-NRCP call for proposals has been postponed. The new deadline is 10 April 2024.</p>"}], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3509608": [{"action": "CERV-2024-NRCP - CERV-LS CERV Lump Sum Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "19 December 2023", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["10 April 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 1600000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2024"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>The objective of this Call is to foster the implementation of the EU Roma strategic framework on equality, inclusion, and participation (EURSF), and of the Council Recommendation, in the Member States.</p><p>Call's aim is to advance the institutional development and capacity of the National Roma Contact Points for Roma equality, inclusion and participation (NRCPs) in their role of facilitating national consultation processes, particularly through reforming and strengthening their established National Roma Platforms (NRPs).</p><p>Projects submitted by consortia formed of NRCP and Roma and pro-Roma civil society organisations are particularly encouraged.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p>&nbsp;<b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-GB\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">:&nbsp;as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-nrcp_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;&#10;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-nrcp_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document.</a></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">3. Proposal page limits and layout:</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/temp-form/af/af_cerv_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">standard proposal template</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">4.&nbsp; &nbsp;Evaluation</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and process are described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-nrcp_en.pd