arget=\"_blank\">Standard proposal template </a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-nrcp_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Call document</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/temp-form/af/detailed-budget-table_cerv-lsii_en.xlsm\" target=\"_blank\">Detailed Budget Table</a> (the budget table can also be downloaded during submission)<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Guide for applicants</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/agr-contr/ls-mga_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Mono/Multi-beneficiary Model Grant Agreement<br />\r\n</a></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><a href=\"https://commission.europa.eu/system/files/2022-12/c_2022_8588_1_en_annexe_acte_autonome_cp_part1_v2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">CERV 2023-2024 work programme</a></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-IE\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2021.156.01.0001.01.ENG&amp;toc=OJ%3AL%3A2021%3A156%3ATOC\" target=\"_blank\">Regulation establishing the CERV Programme</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/guidance/ls-decision_cerv_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision authorising the use of lump sums for actions under the Citizens, Equality, Rights and Values Programme (2021-2027)</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/how-to-manage-your-lump-sum-grants_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Guidance: How to manage your lump-sum grant</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/unit-cost-decision-travel_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision on unit costs for travel and subsistence</a></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/unit-cost-decision-volunteers_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Decision on unit costs for volunteers</a><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "supportInfo": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Please carefully read all provisions of the Call document and get familiar with the proposal template and its annexes before the preparation of your application.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">For help related to this call, please contact&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:EC-CERV-CALLS@ec.europa.eu\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#3366FF\">EC-CERV-CALLS@ec.europa.eu</span></a>&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">or the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://commission.europa.eu/system/files/2023-08/CERV%20Contact%20Points%203%20AUG%202023.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#2897B7\">CERV National Contact Point</span></a>&nbsp;of your country</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Submission of proposals</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\">IT Helpdesk</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/funding-tenders-opportunities/display/OM/Online+Manual\" target=\"_blank\">Online Manual</a> &ndash;&nbsp;Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.</p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of